## API Documentation
- Use OpenAPI/Swagger for REST APIs
- Document all endpoints: method, path, params, body, responses
- Include example requests and responses
- Document error codes and their meanings
- Keep docs in sync with code (prefer auto-generation)

## Architecture Documentation
- Architecture Decision Records (ADRs) for significant decisions
- System diagrams updated quarterly
- Data flow diagrams for complex processes
- Runbooks for operational procedures
- Incident post-mortems documented and shared

## README Template
Every repository MUST include:
1. Project description and purpose
2. Quick start / setup instructions
3. Development workflow
4. Testing instructions
5. Deployment process
6. Architecture overview
7. Contributing guidelines
